snippet.title: FryMinis
snippet.description:
Welcome to FryMinis! I paint miniatures for tabletop roleplaying games and create YouTube videos about improving your Dungeons & Dragons game. I focus on making our hobby a more welcoming and inclusive space for all players through rules clarifications, homebrew and dungeon master advice. I also enjoy unboxing and reviewing the latest D&D products.

If you like what you see, please subscribe so you never miss a video. I love to hear your feedback in the comments. Feel free to send me a message or tweet to let me know what's on your mind. Thanks for checking out FryMinis!
